---
title: Japanese Chicken & Garlic Rice Bowl with Quick-Pickled Onion & Coconut-Chilli Mayo
description: Add tons of flavour to chicken with a tasty sauce mixture, then fill a bowl with garlicky jasmine rice, add the chicken and loads of veggies
and top it all off with pickled onion, crispy shallots and a sensational mayo. This is a recipe for a meal you won't forget!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/japanese-chicken-garlic-rice-bowl-6b1128a6.jpg
